@startuml Taymindis_fcgi-function

skinparam component {
  BackgroundColor<<core>> LightBlue
  BackgroundColor<<config>> LightGreen
  BackgroundColor<<handler>> LightYellow
  BackgroundColor<<external>> LightGray
}

[FastCGI Server] <<external>>
[Application Logic] <<external>>

package "fcgi-function Framework" {
  [ffunc.c] <<core>> as Core
  [ffunc.h] <<config>> as Config
  [Function Handlers] <<handler>> as Handlers
  [Memory Pool] <<core>> as MemPool
  [Thread Management] <<core>> as ThreadMgmt
}

FastCGI Server --> Core : HTTP Requests
Core --> Config : Read Configuration
Core --> MemPool : Allocate/Free Memory
Core --> ThreadMgmt : Manage Threads
Core --> Handlers : Dispatch Requests
Handlers --> Application Logic : Execute Functions

@enduml